### =========================
### PAYMENT FLOW (OTP)
### =========================

### Request payment (generates OTP and sends to email)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/payments/request
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "document": "9999999999",
  "phone": "0987654321",
  "amount": 50
}

### Confirm payment with OTP (replace sessionId and token)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/payments/confirm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "REPLACE_WITH_SESSION_ID",
  "token": "123456"
}

### Get payment session status (replace id)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/payments/session/REPLACE_WITH_SESSION_ID